Package: databoxR
Type: Package
Title: A Smart Explorer for SDTM and ADaM Clinical Trial Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pawan Rama Mali
Maintainer: Pawan Rama Mali <prm@outlook.in>
Description: A Shiny-powered R package that provides a Windows Explorer-style interface 
    for browsing, previewing, and exploring SDTM/ADaM datasets with smart metadata hints. 
    Supports define.xml, CRFs, quick EDA, variable summaries, and CDISC-specific tooling.
